仕事やるから やらせろ
みたいな感じだろ

130
00:11:17.666 --> 00:11:18.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（男性２）マジっすかー？

131
00:11:18.700 --> 00:11:21.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（男性１）決まってんだろ
権力使ってんだよ

132
00:11:21.600 --> 00:11:24.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
職権乱用だっつーの
ハハハ…

133
00:11:24.666 --> 00:11:28.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
この女だけじゃないよ きっと
モデルとか 女優とか

134
00:11:29.133 --> 00:11:31.133  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
他にもいろいろ
やりまくっちゃってんだよ

135
00:11:32.166 --> 00:11:33.833  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ホント ろくでもねえよな

136
00:11:33.933 --> 00:11:36.100  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（男性２）羨ましいっすよねー
ハッハッ…

137
00:11:36.333 --> 00:11:39.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（男性１）大体よ
プロデューサーって なにやってんだ？

138
00:11:40.566 --> 00:11:41.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ただ いるだけだろ

139
00:11:42.033 --> 00:11:44.100  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
“ザギンでシーメー行く？”
とか言って

140
00:11:44.200 --> 00:11:46.033  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
シェルポ乗っちゃったりして
（男性２）ハハハッ

141
00:11:48.466 --> 00:11:51.133  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（男性１）ごちそうさまー
（男性２）ごちそうさまでしたー

142
00:11:51.233 --> 00:11:55.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（男性１）おー まだ早いよ お前
（男性２）はい はい はい…

143
00:12:13.400 --> 00:12:16.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
前岡さんが よく
この白菜漬けの話してて

144
00:12:17.433 --> 00:12:18.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
そうかい

145
00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:20.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
来てますか？

146
00:12:22.133 --> 00:12:22.900  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
いや

147
00:12:40.233 --> 00:12:40.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
フッ…

148
00:12:43.066 --> 00:12:44.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ろくでもないか…

149
00:12:48.600 --> 00:12:53.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
確かに 世間様には なんにも
言い訳できないけどさ

150
00:12:54.833 --> 00:12:57.333  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
その人の才能に ほれるってこと
あるじゃないですか

151
00:12:57.433 --> 00:13:00.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
それが たまたま
こっちが男で 向こうが女で

152
00:13:02.133 --> 00:13:04.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（野瀬）ふとした拍子に…

153
00:13:19.533 --> 00:13:21.733  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
間違ってるってことは
わかってても―

154
00:13:21.833 --> 00:13:24.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
それでも 飛び込んでしまう
気持ちっていうか…

155
00:13:25.933 --> 00:13:26.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
フッ

156
00:13:28.366 --> 00:13:29.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
あるんだよな…

157
00:13:56.900 --> 00:13:59.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（マスター）
月子さんがやってきたのは―

158
00:13:59.400 --> 00:14:02.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
それから１週間ほどたった頃だった

159
00:14:08.700 --> 00:14:09.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（マスター）いらっしゃい

160
00:14:11.733 --> 00:14:12.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
あら？

161
00:14:13.266 --> 00:14:14.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
月ちゃん

162
00:14:18.066 --> 00:14:20.900  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
お酒と白菜漬け ちょうだい

163
00:14:21.600 --> 00:14:22.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（マスター）はいよ

164
00:14:28.900 --> 00:14:31.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
西口のホテルにいるんだけどね

165
00:14:33.566 --> 00:14:35.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
こんなカンヅメ 初めてよ

166
00:14:39.333 --> 00:14:40.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ハッ

167
00:14:41.633 --> 00:14:43.900  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
世の中って面白いよね

168
00:14:46.233 --> 00:14:49.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
こういう時だけ 超売れっ子って
言ってくれんだから

169
00:14:50.033 --> 00:14:51.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（猫の鳴き声）

170
00:14:58.000 --> 00:14:59.266  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（小寿々）メル坊！

171
00:15:19.166 --> 00:15:20.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
野瀬さんはね…

172
00:15:24.866 --> 00:15:27.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
私の作品を
一番わかってくれてる人なの

173
00:15:31.133 --> 00:15:33.733  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
お前のやりたいようにやれって
言ってくれた―

174
00:15:34.700 --> 00:15:36.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
初めてのプロデューサー

175
00:15:41.133 --> 00:15:43.133  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
作品でつながってると―

176
00:15:44.733 --> 00:15:50.633  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
彼の奥さんや子供のことなんか
どうでもよくなってきちゃって…

177
00:15:52.966 --> 00:15:57.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
なんでも
仕事の材料にするんじゃなかったのか？

178
00:16:05.333 --> 00:16:09.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（すすり泣き）

179
00:16:09.566 --> 00:16:10.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ハァ…

180
00:16:12.533 --> 00:16:15.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
そろそろ限界かなあ

181
00:16:24.933 --> 00:16:25.900  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
メル坊

182
00:16:32.000 --> 00:16:32.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（月子）ああ
（武）おお あんた

183
00:16:32.800 --> 00:16:34.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（月子）ねえ 猫 見なかった？

184
00:16:34.666 --> 00:16:36.033  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
今そっちに…
（バイクの急ブレーキ音）

185
00:16:36.133 --> 00:16:37.333  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（メル坊の鳴き声）
（衝突音）

186
00:16:37.433 --> 00:16:38.533  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（月子）メル坊！

187
00:16:38.900 --> 00:16:39.833  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（男性）どうしたの！

188
00:17:00.600 --> 00:17:01.266  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
どうだった？

189
00:17:01.366 --> 00:17:02.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ああ おじさん

190
00:17:02.766 --> 00:17:03.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
どうだったのよ？

191
00:17:04.099 --> 00:17:07.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
うん…
右の後ろ足が折れちゃって―

192
00:17:07.166 --> 00:17:10.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
あとは大丈夫だったみたいだけど
しばらく入院だって

193
00:17:10.266 --> 00:17:12.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ひとまず無事か

194
00:17:12.300 --> 00:17:13.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
うん

195
00:17:13.133 --> 00:17:14.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
よかった… うん

196
00:17:15.466 --> 00:17:17.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
送ってくから乗りな

197
00:17:17.800 --> 00:17:18.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
あ…

198
00:17:28.666 --> 00:17:31.766  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
うまかったよ 白菜漬け

199
00:17:40.666 --> 00:17:41.733  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
おじさん

200
00:17:42.666 --> 00:17:43.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（武）ん？

201
00:17:47.366 --> 00:17:50.866  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
私もね おじさんと故郷 一緒なの

202
00:17:54.566 --> 00:17:55.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
そうかい

203
00:18:04.466 --> 00:18:06.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
泣いてても しょうがないから

204
00:18:09.400 --> 00:18:10.133  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
うん

205
00:18:16.300 --> 00:18:19.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（武）先週 帰った時
海 行ったんだ

206
00:18:20.433 --> 00:18:24.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
そうすっとさ 海岸にカニがいた

207
00:18:26.633 --> 00:18:29.866  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
そんなもん
もう いねえと思ってたらさ

208
00:18:33.600 --> 00:18:35.033  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
生きてたんだ

209
00:18:37.200 --> 00:18:37.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（武）うん

210
00:18:48.566 --> 00:18:54.733  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
♪ あなたの涙は

211
00:18:56.333 --> 00:19:03.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
♪ 青い星のような

212
00:19:08.300 --> 00:19:14.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
♪ 水を湛(たた)える海に

213
00:19:15.200 --> 00:19:20.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
♪ やがて返るでしょう

214
00:19:25.566 --> 00:19:31.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
♪ あなたの心は

215
00:19:31.766 --> 00:19:37.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
♪ あの山の雪のように

216
00:19:42.200 --> 00:19:46.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
♪ 深く積(つ)もり

217
00:19:49.066 --> 00:19:55.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
♪ 閉ざされているのでしょう

218
00:20:06.566 --> 00:20:07.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
やったね

219
00:20:09.733 --> 00:20:11.733  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
面白いよ 文句なしに

220
00:20:13.966 --> 00:20:16.033  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
吹っ切れたのかな？

221
00:20:16.266 --> 00:20:18.333  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
書き出したら止まらなくなった

222
00:20:19.333 --> 00:20:20.900  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
すぐ会社に見せるよ

223
00:20:22.533 --> 00:20:27.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
やっぱり俺たち
作品で証明していくしかないんだよな

224
00:20:30.433 --> 00:20:31.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
もう…

225
00:20:34.266 --> 00:20:35.533  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
終わりにしましょ

226
00:20:41.033 --> 00:20:42.100  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ちょっと待てよ

227
00:20:47.333 --> 00:20:50.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
でないと私 進めない

228
00:21:05.766 --> 00:21:06.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
そっか…

229
00:21:17.466 --> 00:21:18.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
持ってかないの？

230
00:21:21.533 --> 00:21:22.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
受け取れないよ

231
00:21:25.233 --> 00:21:28.266  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
そのホンは 月子自身だから

232
00:21:34.900 --> 00:21:35.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
月子

233
00:21:40.000 --> 00:21:41.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ありがとな

234
00:21:53.066 --> 00:21:54.233  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（ドアが閉まる音）

235
00:22:02.033 --> 00:22:06.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（マスター）半年後 月子さんが書いた
連続ドラマが始まった

236
00:22:08.033 --> 00:22:11.266  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
今度ドラマ 評判いいみたいじゃない

237
00:22:11.366 --> 00:22:12.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
おかげさまで

238
00:22:13.400 --> 00:22:16.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
マスター 私ね 今日デートなの

239
00:22:17.733 --> 00:22:19.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
また？

240
00:22:19.300 --> 00:22:22.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
月ちゃん 懲りないのねえ

241
00:22:22.266 --> 00:22:24.033  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
そんなんじゃないわよ

242
00:22:24.133 --> 00:22:25.533  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（小寿々･月子）フフフ…

243
00:22:25.633 --> 00:22:27.333  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
こんばんは
（マスター）いらっしゃい

244
00:22:27.433 --> 00:22:28.533  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
おっ
（月子）アハッ

245
00:22:32.600 --> 00:22:35.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
マスター白菜漬け 大盛りね

246
00:22:35.900 --> 00:22:36.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
あいよ

247
00:22:41.666 --> 00:22:46.233  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（月子）白菜漬けは 漬ける前に
半日くらい陰干しすると―

248
00:22:46.866 --> 00:22:49.533  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
うまみや甘みが凝縮されます

249
00:22:50.733 --> 00:22:55.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
あとは お好みで
昆布やタカノツメを加えて漬けると―

250
00:22:55.666 --> 00:22:57.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
一層うまくなります

251
00:23:06.466 --> 00:23:07.233  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
では

252
00:23:07.733 --> 00:23:09.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（武･月子）おやすみなさい

253
00:23:09.533 --> 00:23:10.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（メル坊の鳴き声）

254
00:23:10.733 --> 00:23:15.733  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
♪～

255
00:24:24.633 --> 00:24:29.633  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
～♪

